text: József Sarlós (8 July 1909 - 9 July 1996) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nové Zámky District
